content.detailedDescription:
Having a coffee in the garden, noticed a light coming in my direction quite slow. had bright light at one end. it was flashing on one off in about 10 second intervals, 
the i reolized the flashing light was all one end catching the sun which was rising in the east behind me, it was reflecting the sun.
it was a oblong tube shap and it was turning end over end like tumbling and as the reflective end caught the sun it looked like a bright light flashing on and off.
i went for my camera but i could not see it in the view finder screen, i could see where it was going to pass over my home so i focuses my camera on that area and just kept pressing the shutter and captured some images.
it was travelling at a steady speed and hight till it was over head then it turned to the north, not a sharp sudden turn. i watched it go off the the north towards newcastle upon tyne.
content.summary: Came from the east to over head then turned 90 degrees and went north

content.detailedDescription: One white-blue, disk shaped object was observed stationary in the skies over washington, dc. three blinking stop lights were observed next to the apart. building i live at - they are the three towers, which control air traffic over the dc area (washington, dc metropolitan area special flight rules area) right on the montgomery county (chevy chase, friendship heights) md state - dc border.

content.detailedDescription: My friend and i were driving to the gas station, when i saw the first light. this is not the first time we saw the lights, so we slowed down to investigate. the lights were in a triangle formation not moving at all. we went to the gas station and on the way back home we saw four more lights, we watched them hang in the sky for about ten miles worth of driving. at one point we asked the lights jokeingly to do something cool, and almost instantly one light got bright amd blipped out. after that the remaining lights fadded out but never moving. we witnessed them outside of findlay ohio facing due north. i hope other people have seen them. keep looking up ~matt
content.summary: Driving to the gas station.

content.detailedDescription: Got home around 10:20pm. very clear, starry night. i had seen a shooting star 30 min earlier driving home.  i shut off my driveway light just to look at the stars for a minute before going inside.  i saw a plane fly over. it may have been at 10,000 or 15,000 ft.  i could hear the "shhhh" jet sound and see blinking lights, as well as maybe a strobe light on it. but what i could not comprehend was the object in front of it.  maybe 2 or 3 football field lengths in front of that jet traveling at exactly the same speed.  i could see 4 or 5 bright whitish lights, but at that distance not really a shape. it could have been round. the lights were in a small cluster, making me think they were attached to that object. the object, if it was spherical in shape, would have been twice as big as that jet following it.  there were no blinking lights on that object.  i thought it could be two military jets flying close to one another.  i don't think so.  that one in front looked very different from the other.  the pair disappeared behind some trees.  i told my teenage son about it.  we both went outside a few minutes later. we did see another airplane, but it was headed in a different direction, and was way up there, like 30,000 ft.
content.summary: Plane was following an object at exact same speed.  object in front appeared to be larger, at least 4 bright whitish lights, none blinking

content.detailedDescription: Myself and my co driver were en route from thunder bay ontario to cleavland ohio s/b on mn sr61. approximately half way between thunder bay and duluth we pulled into cascade lodge restaurant for coffee and to get warmed up. this we needed to do as the alternator in the freightliner we were driving had quit working and we needed whatever power we had in the batteries to run the lights so the cab was very cold. my partner left the window table where we were seated for about five minutes or so. during that time i turned to gaze out of the window and immediately noticed some type of object with lights from one end to the other just hovering sort of parked in mid air just visible above the shoreline trees. fascinated and mesmerized i couldn't take my eyes off it. during the time i watched first one then another light, orb like i suppose, appeared to come out of the underside of this object and slowly descend until they went out of sight below the treeline. as i recall the lights on the main, larger object were white and the two lights that descended appeared the same colour. in fact it almost seemed that the lights that left the larger object were at first some of those that were on the hovering object but as they left none of the main object's lights disappeared so i had reasoned at that time the detached lights were in fact something separate. i did not see the two separate lights again. the large object slowly descended below the tree tops out of my sight and did not reappear. i was stunned at what i just saw and then at that time and still to this day believe i saw a ufo. i did not mention this to my partner then or ever and i have only recently mentioned it to my kids. it has always remained in my memory although not quite as clear as that night but not so fleeting as to wonder what i believe i witnessed. as an afterthought, i had never considered any connection between the ufo and our loosing the alternator that night until very recently while reading accounts of others experiences where vehicle electrics became an issue. can't be sure to this day if the two occurrences are related as the alternator had quit prior to this event but what do i know? i did not have a camera at the time so i have no photos. i have searched the internet however and found some images that very closely resemble what i saw.
content.summary: Observed ufo just above tree tops. observed two lights/orbs decend from the main unit to below treetops.

content.detailedDescription: I was at clingmans dome in the smoky mountains and taking pictures of the scenery when i noticed a big odd green spot in the middle of my screen so didn't take a picture,  i couldn't see it with my naked eye so just assumed there was something going on with my camera so i cleaned my lens,  looked all around to see if someone was using something that could reflect this light but didn't see anything. so i just continued to take pictures all around the dome and wasn't really paying any attention or noticing anything i thought whatever was going wrong was fixed,  i was up there for about twenty minutes.  so on my way home and looking over my pictures and started to see the green spot still and in a lot of the pictures from just one area of the mountains not in the others.  the photos containing the green light  were all taken from about 4:54 to 5:05.  as i was looking at them i noticed that i took many successive photos and it was in different spots in all of the pictures.   so i was wondering what it could be,  maybe a drone or something.   i also took a snapchat video (really poor quality) of the view and happened to catch it moving erratically. after zooming in on the pictures it appears to change shape and have some lights or dots in some then spikes in others.   it also looks like it is behind things in some pictures and sometimes in front of things and sometimes it is almost see through as if it was dissolving. i tried to logically debunk it but nothing i thought of makes sense.  maybe it's some kind of gas or drone,  just not sure so i decided to submit these photos and the video to see if anyone else can make sense of this or has seen anything else like it.
content.summary: At clingmans dome taking multiple pictures of scenery

content.detailedDescription: Driving on 128 southbound, 9:30 pm est, 11-16-15, noticed a white light with a tear drop shape descending from the sky very fast. object "blinked out". the object appeared to leave a trail of some sort, but again, it "streaked" across the sky in a descending direction. object was noticed to the south west. my first impression was that this was a meteor, a piece of space junk, a fireball, or firework. however, after considering all of the above, definitely not a firework or meteor. i never lost sight of the object as it appeared to have "winked out".
content.summary: Tear-drop shaped bright light descending very fast and then disappeared

content.detailedDescription:
The video included is from tonight, november 16 2015, because it was compressed it may not as clearly show what i saw. i have already submitted something in 2014 about the same ufo but never pursued the case. after seeing it once or twice a week i've finally decided to do something about it. it always comes from the same place (north, from the lake, towards somewhere south) tonight i just saw it while driving. here is my last account that may give more insight from may 2 2014 
"we were driving down bullheadly road (this is in tallahassee florida) at about 9 pm when i saw two bright lights, brighter and different from any airplane lights i've seen. i told the driver of the car to keep going and not turn so we can see what it was. as we got closer and closer (we are on a road heading right for a lake called lake iamonia) we noticed that it was not moving, seemingly hovering. we went right to the lake from and parked with our lights on. it was hovering at the center of the lake. i am not sure how big it exactly was, but it wasn't small, and it was hovering about 200 feet up. it had two main bright lights on its wings and a smaller white light on the front. we watched it for about 5 minutes, just sitting there hovering. i decided to take a picture of it to show people, but i forgot to turn off the flash. right after i flashed the camera (the photo is not that good) it started coming toward us. we were still interested, so we rolled down the window to get a look. the sound was a quiet drone, almost like an airplane that is very, very high up in the sky ( just a reminder again, it wasn't high in the sky at all). it wasn't going fast to start out with, but when it went over us and we turned around to follow it, it spend up gradually to a speed we could not even match with our car. we also noticed as it was over us that there definitely was two wings, on the side of it there was small red lights, and it was a sharp triangle. that was the last we saw of it, going out into the distance."
this and the rest of my accounts have been nearly identical, it is very clearly not a plane. it is too low and too slowly moving. my only explanation is an oddly large drone. considering it is about the size of about two compact cars, it would have to be one unique drone and would not be some civilian tech. it is here all the time around the same time, i just want to know what it is.
content.summary: Ufo yet again seen in leon county

content.detailedDescription: At approximately 6:30 pm i was at my home near sr56 facing north and i was about to walk into my garage when i noticed what i thought was an airplane of chopper in the sky traveling east to west, about 50 - 60 degrees off the horizon, which is where i usually see planes in the tpa flight path. i thought it was odd because unlike the other planes, this one had no strobe lights or colored lights, it was the color of a flare. i thought it might be the iss, but the time i saw that it was white reflecting the sun and traveling west to east. it looked very much like a meteor except if it was then it was very high up because its apparent speed was like that of an aircraft. i thought it might be a missile being launched from the east coast of florida, but it was further north than the space shuttles i've seen launching almost due east from my location. since it looked like it was near the airport's approach path i thought it might be a sam except that it flew in a straight line and did not waver. i kept watching it for about 30 seconds until it either went behind a cloud in the west, burnt out, or turned off. the brightness of the object did not vary at all and nothing fell off of it.
content.summary: Yellow flare-colored object or meteor traveling west to east

content.detailedDescription: I was jogging in the bronx by the marina del ray catering hall which is by the throgs neck and whitestone bridge when i looked up and saw a brigth light with a white trail of something coming from the back of the light...The ball of light was acsending towards the sun.It reminded me of something i heard at my aunts funeral the night before. he said somehow my aunt would give me a sign that she was alright. the image of the light ascending to the sun reminded me of my aunts spirit acsending to heaven.So i snapped 2 pictures. i didnt want to get cold so i continued jogging along my way. when i got home i looked at the photos. i posted them to my facebook without really noticing anything. i wrote about my aunt and the comparison to what the priest had said...But it wasnt till later when i enlarged the 2 pictures that i noticed i caught something pretty amazing.I have enclosed 4 pictures. the first 2 are the pictues as i took them and the last 2 are the pictures enlarged and focused on the white ball of light. what is this!!!?
content.summary: A ball of light acsending towards the sun slowly

content.detailedDescription:
Walking in a neighborhood being developed near where i grew up.  roads had been paved and there were frames for new homes and some completed homes.  time was night. date was sometime in the summer of 1996, but not sure.  

three lights streaked across the sky up and to my right and then came to a complete stop - amber colored.  no sound could be heard but i was at a distance to where, if it was an airplane or helicopter, i wouldn't have heard it anyway.  it moved at a phenomenal speed, faster than any object imaginable.  the stop was immediate, it didn't take time to slow down.  the three lights were affixed as if they were all of the points of a triangle.  i never saw any object, just the lights. 

the lights continued to move in the same direction from the complete stop at the same phenomenal speed - never needed time to speed up.  moved across roughly 20% of my field of view before stopping again - immediate stop.  after the second stop, object moved in the complete opposite direction (going west)at the same high speed and then came to a third immediate stop, again never needing time to speed up from the stop or slow down from movement.   

after the third stop, object continued at same high speed in the reverse direction (original direction - going east) until gone from my sight.  entire event happened in less than four seconds.
content.summary: Appeared moving east at amazing speed, stopped completely then continued again.  stopped a second time before going in opposite direction and then stopped a third time.  continued moving east after third stop and streaked across sky and out of sight.

content.detailedDescription: On august 27, 1964 around 9:30pm, my father,mother and me were watching the 1964 democractic national convention on tv when my father took the trash outside in the backyard to the incinator,shortly thereafter my mother & i heard my father call to us to come out to the backyard. we did and he told us to look-up,when we did we saw a levitating metallic craft slowly moving from north west to southeast at tree top. i can clearly remember the top dome portion had rectangle windows that you could peer through(transparent )and lighted from the inside like a hallway. it also had white lights on the center seam. we continue to watch until it went behind some buildings! i was 5 years old when this happened i'm 58 now, besides the craft itself, the most mysterious thing was that nobody in the neighborhood saw anything. nothing!, during that time that area was very populated , somebody should have seen something.....It was my thought that "they" have power to block thing!.....James lattiemore
content.summary: A disc shaped metallic craft levitated at tree-top level before us foe about 15 minutes until disappeared behind  nearby buildings

content.detailedDescription:
I was in bed resting. i frequently awaken between the hours of two to four am.  i was lying on my back in my bed when i noticed to my left the white light being. humanoid but tall and thin.  with no sound the being reached into my left chest area, i didn't feel any pain, pressure or discomfort.  that lasted about 5 minutes.  the being removed it's hand from my left chest and stood there for about 2 minutes and then vanished.  no crafts, a solo being.

i felt fine the next few months however a strong intuitive urge kept hounding me to get to the cardiologist.  again, no chest pains or anything.
i to get an ekg they ordered a stress test, then read the test and they informed me of my dyer health condition.  so i was rushed into the hospital to prep me for a triple bypass and a replacement aorta valve.  i was born bicuspid instead of tricuspid.  it was a triple bypass and a aorta valve replacement, they joked and said a two for one operation deal since they sawed my chest opened.

my take and feelings on this incident was the white light being made temporary repairs for me to not have a heart attack or stroke ahead of time.  the doctors were saying your so lucky because the bicuspid one valve was completely clogged and your heart valves for the bypass' were also clogged in bad shape that i got into the hospital at the right time.  it was a miracle.  all the while the white light being made adjustments to give me the time and the strong intuition to get into the hospital to save my life.

i have the closest image of the white light being i could find anywhere and a photo of a man sleeping like i would have that night.

ps i don't dream of being in my bedroom. when i dream i dream of going vast distances, seeing other things, never did i have a dream of myself in my bed.
content.summary: Whit light being reached inside my left chest. i was lying on my back. when light being removed it's hand from my chest it vanished. interdimential, no crafts, solo being.

content.detailedDescription:
I went to pick my daughter up from her school at 3pm, i arrived at 2.30pm to get a parking space. i sat and out of my window i see a cloud that looked like an elephant, i opened my window and took a photo on my phone and sent it to my wife, when i looked at it again i see an object to the left of the picture. i looked back up to yhe cloud and see the object was still there and not moving, there was no noise or movement it was just sitting there.
there were airplanes flying by that looked about the same size, i left to go home at 3.10pm and the object was still there.
content.summary: Took a picture of a cloud and see an object in the photo, when i looked up it was still there, the object was still there when i left to go home.

content.detailedDescription: I  went out of my house to leave the rubbish bin at the end of my drive.It was around 7pm dark with a fairly cloud free starlit sky. my attention was drawn to an unusual multi coloured object which i at first thought must be some sort of aircraft in the northeastern sky.As i observed this anomaly it seemed to move vertically and laterally in random bursts whilst emitting intense bursts of very bright coloured light ranging from red,yellow,blue,green and white. i further observed through binos and confirmed at least that it wasn't an aircraft and it certainly was unlike anything i had ever seen in the night sky
content.summary: This was a multi coloured object flashing red green,white, and yellow. it definitely appeared to move randomly and the lights were extremely intense

content.detailedDescription: I was on a bus and it stopped at a traffic light, and i looked out the opposite window when a dull grey object in the middle of the sky caught my attention, i was very confused and i waited for it to do something so that i could identify it (like a bird or a plane) but it simply remained in the same place. it had the shape of a regular trapezium, it had no wings or lights or a trail of any sort, it was a plain grey shape. the bus moved a little forward and with this slight movement i saw another angle of the object, which reflected the sunlight on its bottom left corner and seemed to fade at the sides, which then gave me the impression that it had a disc-like shape. also because the bus moved very little, i thought that it must have been very far away because its angle changed a lot. the weather was clear that day too so i didn't know what it could have been. when i tried to reach for my phone to take a photo, the bus had started moving again.
content.summary: The object appeared far away and it was stationary, in the sky and high above the closest buildings, it reflected the sunlight

content.detailedDescription: From the first night i moved into my current residence i have been observing these objects.  there is no consistency like you would have with planets or other celestial objects.  it will occur for several nights in a row and then sometimes will not reoccur for months or years.  at times it has made sudden moves such as getting out of the way of an airplane.  one of the first encounters involved the object being fairly close to my position and when i went into the house to get my telescope it moved away to a farther position before i could get back through the door.  a friend who was visiting actually saw it move.  another odd occurrence was when i was outside with my wife watching a thunder storm.  there was lightning and no other objects were visible in the sky. suddenly, the flashing object appeared as i had seen many times before. it was the only object in the sky.  the it disappeared just as suddenly after the storm subsided. there have been numerous other events over the years.  in the last year i finally got a camera that could capture some of he events. i have taken numerous pictures and videos on my camera documenting some of these behaviors.  i am including a very small sample of pictures.  i could not get the videos to attach.  note the first two pictures which were taken on a tripod with a delay so the camera was not being touched at the time the pictures were taken.  the object changed shape within a few seconds. i would very much like to talk to an investigator and to show him more of my pictures and video
content.summary: Multiple events over several years with vrying behaviors

content.detailedDescription:
It was around 9:20 pm on nov 15 2015 when out walking my dog i heard a sound. it sounded like a car door or house door i thought and i turned around toward the northeast when i noticed a round light that was not real bright moving fast toward the ne. i thought it may be a drone but never could confirm or deny it being a drone. it appeared right over our heads about 20 or so feet above us. it had a tail that was glowing. it did not look like a flame (it was a lot whiter(brighter) than the orb that was more the color of a light bulb) but was about 12 inches long following the orb that seemed to be the size of a baseball.It only lasted a few seconds and either accelerated or just blinked out. it happened so fast. there were 3 airplanes in the sky while this happened but they were way up in the sky and were east of where we were.
i do not know if the noise i heard came from the orb but could not find any source for the noise that got my attention to turn around.
content.summary: Was out with dog when i heard something. i turned around and saw this right above my head

content.detailedDescription: Sun came up from behind a dark bank of thick clouds. sun was reflecting off of the water. i took a picture. at the time i did not see the object due to the bright relection off of the water. the picture shows a bright object between myself and the dark clouds. i enlarged the picture and bright lightss on the surface appeared. i had taken 2 pictures a few seconds apart. the second picture shows the object had ascended some and the pattern of lights had changed. i was shocked when i saw the detail of the object. due to the brightness of the relection of the sun on the water i did not directly observe the object. i noticed it first on the two photos i took. there was nothing else between me and the dark cloud bank except the ocean. the pictures are on my phone which i can not attach to this report.
content.summary: Took a picture over the ocean and it appeared on the snapshot

content.detailedDescription: While this incident took place over a year ago i am on reporting it now because of watching recent things on tv, and due to the fact that it has continued to bother my fiance and i quite a bit sense. i wanted to report this when it happened but she persuaded me not to,for one i am friends with the sheriff and a little league coach in our community! although we did tell some relatives. first i would like to say that i am not in any way some person looking for attention or some ufo person that might make things up, i never believed in too much of it although have been open to the idea of other life but what we seen that night could (not) and was not either from this world or a technology that we are unaware of. my fiance and i were fishing one night on a small lake in central michigan around 3 am in the morning, and no we we were not drinking  (yet) it was a completely beautiful evening with not a single cloud in the sky we had just launched the boat and had just made our first cast when i just seem to be lucky or unlucky when i was looking up at the stars out of nowhere it seemed as if this light that came out of a black hole if i could describe it that way and it was brighter than anything i've ever seen i then went to  scream to my fiance but at the same time she was screaming back to me do you see this it was coming straight down and getting brighter and brighter and bigger and bigger when it started making a pulsating sound that we could almost feel kind of like a woomp woomp woomp sound, when coming to a stop.It stayed stationary for about 2 seconds,then a different sound was made and it shot off to the west i would say covering a 100 miles or so within a second then it stopped again and came back the exact same path at the same speed, my fiance at that point screamed and dropped her phone because she was trying to record.It then made another sound almost directly above us got really really bright again and then ascended almost immediately out of sight! i do give my  word that everything i have stated is 100% the truth nor is exaggerated i consider myself to be an intelligent man and can differentiate things that go in a straight line that others might perceive as a ufo this was in no way  meteor asteroid nor was it anything man made as far as i know militarily speaking. just decided to make this report now to get it our my chest. i do not have any mental disorders nor does my fiance we know what we saw that evening and unfortunately now can not drive walk outside go fishing or do anything at night without staring at the sky,lol well thanks for reading sincerely and truthfully shawn vanhoose and jackylin chamberlin
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering,Other
content.summary: Fiance and i fishing on a small lake which we commonly do when a knight rider them the moon came directly out of nowhere headed towards the earth and came to an abrupt stop making a pulsating sound that we could  see an almost feel

content.detailedDescription:
We were camping in black kaspian campgrounds outside of tahoe city ca. noticed an unfamiliar glow filtering through the dense pine trees. we began to hike towards the light, curious to what it was. the light seemed to elude us as we navigated through the trees. coming to a clearing at the bottom of a fairly steep hill, the light(s) appeared to radiate from a ridge approx. 100 yards up the rise. we hiked upward in random direction, separating by a distance of a few hundred feet. i began experiencing chills and a sensation of dread. my girl was climbing at a faster pace than me, and angling off at a greater distance. i noticed very bright lights streaming from above. they scanned back and forth from my position to where my friend was, blinding me as they focused on me. my friend was enveloped in a glowing haze as the lights brushed past her. i was overcome by a intense fear and a sense of warning to leave the area. reluctantly, my girl started down toward me,angry that i had been screaming 'let's go'. she also had witnessed the intense lights, but reasoned it to be sunlight filtering through the brush. the sun was setting low behind the mountain, so i didn't accept her explanation and convinced her that we should return to our camp before dark.
at approx. 3 am we decided to hike a little in the woods. i took my camera,an average priced vivitar digital flash.We had a couple of halogen flashlights that put out bright light. the moonlight was enough to adjust our eyes to be able to see. the flashlights we used at random when we heard noises or such. i held my camera at arms length and snapped pictures at random. the bright flash of the camera lit up the forest in random direction every minute or so. after an hour or so, we headed back toward camp. it was at this time a light swooshed overhead and 'melted' into the trees ahead. it hovered a few hundred feet away in the forest, but three distinct lights shone through the darkness. i took some photos and hurried towards camp. in the final half a mile or so i snapped random pictures in every direction.
back at camp we set up a makeshift perimeter that encircled our tent. viewing the photos that night produced nothing but sleep for our tired eyes.
several times until the daylight arrived, we heard the snap crackle of footsteps around the tent, but were not up to investigating. we were in bear and big cat country, so decided the tent was safety.
it wasn't until i returned home and downloaded my camera onto my computer that i discovered what we experienced. the random photographs taken that night in the woods had captured images of what i believe are alien beings. these photos are 100% legitimate, real and unadulterated. the photos clearly show an alien staring at us from behind a tree. the face is captured in the realism you would expect from someone who had a flashbulb erupt in their face. undeniable evidence. i have photos that show this , or more, aliens that presumably followed or trailed us to camp. a total of seven snapshots clearly show non human entities. these pictures are not faked photo shopped, or confused with something else. expert analysis will verify that indeed something other than human has been captured on film and exist as living beings.
content.summary: Light appeared overhead then hovered in distance, while hiking in the woods

content.detailedDescription:
My friend and i were riding our bikes around 9:30 pm on an august evening a few years ago. our subdivision is small about 1 mile in a divided circle shape...There are no street lamps around the back part of this circle...Just a gravel road and the homes on fairly big properties (1 acre apprx) 

it was a very dark night and my friend and i were talking and laughing. ..Being 24 yrs of age. 

i first noticed a bright light in front of one of the homes about 40 ft in front of us.. and made a comment about that interesting light fixture. all of a sudden the light rises up and becomes brighter and pulses a blue-white light.

my friend and i screamed at the top of our lungs and peddled our bikes quickly back home. as i looked back this light, brilliant as ever...Quickly zoomed up and out toward the back of the house and vanished in thin air. 

when we reached my house we were in hysterics and could not make sense of this event.
content.summary: Riding our bikes in neighborhood.  noticed glowing blue light at neighbour's front door. we made a comment on that aloud. glowing orb flew up and over home.

content.detailedDescription: On friday november 13, 2015 at approximately 6:10 pm est, i was taking pictures of the crescent moon looking from amelia island towards jacksonville.  upon reviewing the pictures i noticed the flume in three of the photos.  it was not seen during the taking of the photos.  upon reviewing the photos and zooming the photos on the flume there is a cylinder shaped object.  the three photos submitted were all taken with in a minute or two of each other.
content.summary: Traveled from the right of the moon to the left

content.detailedDescription: Hi guy , it was a great experience when i saw four flash light above a building ..It is early morning time at 5:30 am ist approx i heard some noise like a plane but it not sound like a plane do,it is differnt from a plane noise and its is continuously making noise then i wear my jacket and went up on the terrace to identify the source of the noise but i not found anything and then suddenly i look around and seen four blue flash light above a building ,i never seen this kind of light ever in my location i usually watched alien encounter on discovery and seen this kind of light in shows...The least ght of four flash beam light is very intensive and very bright,then i slowly get down and took my phone to capture a image of the light and after capturing the images i called my mother and sister and they also found this lights are in a straight line and very bright and we continuously watching those four light above the building and suddenly it disappear after few mintues when i start pointing it out to my family.....
content.summary: Flash light seen in chandigarh in a straight line after a big noise

content.detailedDescription:
I was hunting and sat to wait for game.  just before dark a saskwatch entered the cut block,went to the middle and stopped. before i could move or think a large black shape appeared, shone a light on it and both disappeared.
i'm over 60 and have seen ufos twice before. but this just blew my mind.
are saskwatch some kind of ufos scouts or explorers?

.
content.summary: Sighted saskwatch   ufo hovered and lite up saskwatch   both were gone

content.detailedDescription: On vacation (tucson az) playing golf, watched and heard f18's flying around courses a lot that day, took picture of friend and saw craft in photo it made no sound unlike f18's, it was so far off i didn't think it was a craft, (maybe a bird) plus made no sound so i  went back to playing golf. later that evening was looking at image with friend and we decided it had to be a craft of some kind. i worked for general dynamics for few years and watched a lot of military aircraft flying and this looked nothing like any i have observed. it appeared to be ascending in a straight line at about a 20 degree angle.
content.summary: On vacation playing golf, watched and heard f18's flying around courses a lot, took picture of friend and saw craft in photo it made no sound unlike f18's

content.detailedDescription:
Driving into florence.
observed several rocket like things in the sky,flying in two different directions. watched for about twenty minutes as they flew in the sky. i thought they were strange to be flying so close together.Don't know what they were,just curious. also previous night saw three lights in the night sky, about 645, in triangle formation, then separated. then they started to fall and were sparking. this was in fort mitchell.3
content.summary: 8 rocket like things in the sky,flying in two different directions, close together.
